    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究发现，英国 47 亿英镑的庇护法案需要当地解决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/uk-s-4-7-billion-asylum-bill-requires-local-fix-study-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家研究机构提议，英国政府应该将安置寻求庇护者的责任转交给地方机构，因为住宿费用飙升占用了其他项目的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/uk-s-4-7-billion-asylum-bill-requires-local-fix-study-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国经济勉强增长，韩国央行评估风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/south-korea-s-economy-ekes-out-growth-to-emerge-from-contraction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国经济在早前出现萎缩后，上个季度勉强维持增长，凸显出出口增长放缓、地缘政治紧张局势加剧以及美国总统竞选可能对依赖贸易的国家造成影响的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/south-korea-s-economy-ekes-out-growth-to-emerge-from-contraction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 23:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国与中国关系恶化，印度却向其示好：值得关注的点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/germany-is-courting-india-as-ties-with-china-sour-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与中国的关系恶化给德国的经济前景蒙上阴影，德国正试图将印度培养为贸易和地缘政治支持的来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/germany-is-courting-india-as-ties-with-china-sour-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨格称肯尼亚准备捍卫当前先令汇率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/kenya-prepared-to-defend-shilling-at-current-levels-thugge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚央行行长卡马乌·图格 (Kamau Thugge) 表示，今年先令汇率在创下世界最高纪录后，目前处于适当水平，政策制定者准备动用创纪录的外汇储备来捍卫先令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/kenya-prepared-to-defend-shilling-at-current-levels-thugge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行观察人士认为 10 月不会有变化，一半人预计 12 月会有所变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boj-watchers-see-no-october-move-with-half-expecting-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[接受彭博调查的大多数经济学家表示，日本央行预计将于下周维持基准利率不变，并于12月或1月加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boj-watchers-see-no-october-move-with-half-expecting-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔毒枭被捕为诺沃亚在危机中助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/arrest-of-top-ecuador-drug-lords-hands-noboa-much-needed-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瓜亚基尔电视台袭击案两名嫌疑人在西班牙被捕，此次袭击事件成为全球头条新闻，并引发了厄瓜多尔打击黑帮的战争，这给厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚在严重的电力危机中提供了急需的鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/arrest-of-top-ecuador-drug-lords-hands-noboa-much-needed-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
